snippet.title: Parking World | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The cat... err car is out of the bag! 🐈 Our new game Parking World is ready to wishlist on Steam. 🚗

👉https://links.aerosoft.com/parkingworld

Build your own lot, manage your car park and solve all parking problems in seven unique scenarios!

Check out our Teaser Trailer!

We also invite you to join the official Parking World Discord server to be able to participate in the development process. 
👉https://discord.gg/NMC6nKANvV
